snippet.title: Super Mario Starshine - 2023 Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Mario Starshine Discord Server:
https://discord.gg/2Qzqn3WGfY

Before you even mention it, yes I am aware that the Title Screen in this trailer still shows the year 2022. Now you can read the rest of the description! :]

Here's a brand new Super Mario Starshine Trailer! I decided to make this trailer since it's been about a year since I made the last trailer if you don't count the Demo Release. Unfortunately there is no new Demo to play or anything like that. I just felt like releasing a new trailer for the sake of showing how much progress we've been making with this hack. Just in case you're unaware, Super Mario Starshine is a modification for Super Mario Galaxy 2 that aims to make Sunshine levels playable in the Galaxy 2 engine.

Bianco Hills Remix (Trailer Theme): https://youtu.be/BbaFo9D7KAY

Shine Mod by Froggo: https://youtube.com/channel/UCiyIBAMGwkgvlc2uIIIikTg

Social Links and Stuff:
My Discord - https://discord.gg/3xvcveZ
My Twitter - https://twitter.com/SPG642
My Twitch - https://www.twitch.tv/spg64

#SuperMarioGalaxy #SuperMarioGalaxy2 #SuperMarioSunshine

Thanks for watching my stuff! :D
